5: Hey, er, are you guys still open?
9: Um... I'll have today's special, I guess.
12:
Is it just me, or is the vibe here kinda... 
heavy?
16:
We ought not to stay long. 
In fact, we should take our leave right now.
24:
Hands where I can see them! 
The Guild Knights have you surrounded!
25:
Don't try to resist—
we've received intel that this place is a 
front for dealing in black market 
cursed gear!
32:
H-hey, you've got the wrong guy! 
I'm just here to eat!
35:
Save your excuses for the judge, 
criminal. 
We know all about your little 
misadventures!
36:
You're the adventurer working under 
Pur Lilie, right? We've had our eyes on 
you for some time now.
39:
That's an entirely different matter, isn't 
it? Don't you think this is a bit unfair?
42:
Unfair? 
That's enough out of you, fiend!
49:
N-now, now! 
We'll cooperate, so let's take it easy, 
okay?
52:
Enough outta you! 
It's time you punks learned a lesson—
55:
What the hell were you thinking? 
Is Nimbus rubbing off on you?
59:
I'm sorry, Light... 
I kinda just snapped after seeing what 
they did to you. 
Anyway, we should probably get a 
move on.
64:
Not so fast there, friends. 
Your would-be escape ends here.
67:
Watch out, Commander Finn! 
These two are stronger than they look!
69:
Of course. 
They broke through our defenses 
without a hitch, didn't they?
73: Let us go. We don't want any trouble!
77:
You're rather skilled with that. 
But unfortunately for you, it appears 
you lack experience against other 
sabreurs.
84:
We've gotten ourselves into a pickle 
this time, huh?
88:
You'll need to answer for wielding your 
blade against the authorities, but I'd 
advise against speaking of Starview.
92:
Sorry, Light... 
We should be trying to get you back to 
your world. It's all my fault we're dealing 
with this instead...
95:
It's fine. 
No journey is complete without a few 
setbacks along the way.
100:
You're free to go, so come on out. 
And... if it's all right, I wish to make 
amends.
108:
There they are! 
I was SO worried about you two!
111: Wait, so you bailed us out?
114:
Hee-hee! 
Let's just say I've got some connections 
with some of the top brass in the guild...
115:
And it just so happens that the guild 
oversees the force that locked you up! 
Just goes to show it's all about who you 
know in this world, right?
120:
While that may be true in some cases, 
you had nothing to do with this.
127:
While it's true that you and your 
companions are currently persons of 
interest to the guild, your arrest was 
due to a clerical error on our end.
129:
Not only that, but you were subjected 
to violent misconduct by members of 
our force during your confrontation. 
This should have never happened.
131:
I would like to personally apologize 
for how the situation was handled, 
especially regarding our use of 
violence.
134:
Oh, uh, it's fine! 
All's well that ends well, right?
137:
I'm glad an honorable man such as 
yourself is in charge.
143:
Pur Lilie. Understand that your 
connection to this incident has only 
heightened our suspicions.
144:
Now, these are merely my own 
conjectures, but I'd wager you and the 
guild are taking advantage of the 
system somehow.
145:
Do you understand the harm that 
would do for our organization? 
We have to uphold the public's trust.
154:
However, as a Guild Knight, I must set 
my own biases aside.
156: I just find it all to be very suspicious.
161:
Allow us to clear those suspicions for 
you.
163:
We'll show you the truth... 
but only if you promise to stay quiet 
about it.
170:
Y-yes... 
It's certainly unexpected, to say the 
least.
173:
Your intentions have been made clear 
to me.
175:
Of course, whether you're engaging in 
illegal activities with Pur Lilie is a 
different story.
178:
You're welcome to visit us whenever 
you like.
181:
In a non-professional capacity, 
of course.
185: He really is a man of his word...
188:
Farewell for now. 
I will look forward to my next time off.
